1108
00:51:36.330 --> 00:51:37.740
<font color="#00ffff">Herzlichen Dank, Herr Haas.</font>

1109
00:51:38.420 --> 00:51:39.380
<font color="#00ffff">Zuerst Herr Udry</font>
